[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 11790,
        "end_time": 16001,
        "text": "Your interstellar police squad\nhas tracked a group of dangerous rebels"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 16001,
        "end_time": 19681,
        "text": "to a cluster of of seven small planets."
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 19681,
        "end_time": 24462,
        "text": "Now you must apprehend them quickly \nbefore their reinforcements arrive."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 24462,
        "end_time": 27191,
        "text": "Of course, the rebels won\u2019t just stay put."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 27191,
        "end_time": 31433,
        "text": "They\u2019ll try to dodge you\nby moving from planet to planet."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 31433,
        "end_time": 34201,
        "text": "But you have one major advantage."
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 34201,
        "end_time": 40460,
        "text": "Every hour, your state-of-the-art cruiser \ncan warp between any two planets,"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 40460,
        "end_time": 42409,
        "text": "while their beat-up smuggling ship"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 42409,
        "end_time": 46491,
        "text": "can only jump to an adjacent planet \nin that same time."
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 46491,
        "end_time": 48843,
        "text": "These rebels don\u2019t like to stay put."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 48843,
        "end_time": 52291,
        "text": "Every time they can relocate, they will."
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 52291,
        "end_time": 57513,
        "text": "Your scouts tell you that the approaching\nrebel fleet is 10 hours away."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 57513,
        "end_time": 60592,
        "text": "You can\u2019t risk letting the rebels escape."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 60592,
        "end_time": 63514,
        "text": "Can you devise a sequence \nfor searching the planets"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 63514,
        "end_time": 67772,
        "text": "that\u2019s guaranteed to catch them \nin 10 warps or less,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 67772,
        "end_time": 72582,
        "text": "no matter what moves they make?"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 72582,
        "end_time": 74866,
        "text": "Rounding up the rebels won\u2019t be easy."
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 74866,
        "end_time": 79926,
        "text": "For one, you have no way of knowing which \nplanet they\u2019re on to begin with."
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 79926,
        "end_time": 85222,
        "text": "And without that information, it\u2019s hard \nto determine where they\u2019ll move next."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 85222,
        "end_time": 87103,
        "text": "So where do you begin?"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 87103,
        "end_time": 91241,
        "text": "When tackling problems of this kind \nit often helps to simplify things,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 91241,
        "end_time": 94681,
        "text": "so you can better understand \ntheir dynamics."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 94681,
        "end_time": 97440,
        "text": "Let\u2019s imagine that this cluster \nhas the same arrangement"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 97440,
        "end_time": 102540,
        "text": "but no outermost planets,\nleaving only the four in the center."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 102540,
        "end_time": 105391,
        "text": "We still don\u2019t know which planet \nthe rebels start on."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 105391,
        "end_time": 107529,
        "text": "But there\u2019s one key feature:"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 107529,
        "end_time": 111252,
        "text": "the third planet \nis adjacent to all others,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 111252,
        "end_time": 115206,
        "text": "which means the rebels either start there \nand move somewhere else,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 115206,
        "end_time": 117485,
        "text": "or start on one of the other planets"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 117485,
        "end_time": 122140,
        "text": "and have no choice \nbut to move to planet three."
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 122140,
        "end_time": 129031,
        "text": "Simply checking planet three\ntwice in a row would do the trick."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 129031,
        "end_time": 133421,
        "text": "Adding the three outer planet \nadds a bit more complexity,"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 133421,
        "end_time": 135852,
        "text": "but the same strategy remains."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 135852,
        "end_time": 141051,
        "text": "We want to check the planets in an order \nthat will eventually corner the rebels."
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 141051,
        "end_time": 143343,
        "text": "And there\u2019s another insight \nthat can help us:"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 143343,
        "end_time": 146792,
        "text": "each hour, the rebels move from \nan even-numbered planet"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 146792,
        "end_time": 148762,
        "text": "to an odd-numbered planet,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 148762,
        "end_time": 150530,
        "text": "or vice versa."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 150530,
        "end_time": 152770,
        "text": "This gives us a way \nto simplify the problem"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 152770,
        "end_time": 155742,
        "text": "by dividing the planets into two subsets,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 155742,
        "end_time": 158170,
        "text": "and tackling each one separately."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 158170,
        "end_time": 162392,
        "text": "For starters, let\u2019s assume the rebels \nbegin on an even-numbered planet:"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 162392,
        "end_time": 163110,
        "text": "either two,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 163110,
        "end_time": 163868,
        "text": "four,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 163868,
        "end_time": 165191,
        "text": "or six."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 165191,
        "end_time": 167582,
        "text": "So we\u2019ll search planet two first."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 167582,
        "end_time": 170533,
        "text": "If they\u2019re not there, they must have \nstarted on either four"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 170533,
        "end_time": 171843,
        "text": "or six."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 171843,
        "end_time": 173690,
        "text": "which means they can move to three,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 173690,
        "end_time": 174491,
        "text": "five,"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 174491,
        "end_time": 176119,
        "text": "or seven."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 176119,
        "end_time": 180182,
        "text": "Planet three at the center gives them \nthe most options for their next move,"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 180182,
        "end_time": 182623,
        "text": "so we\u2019ll want to check there next."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 182623,
        "end_time": 185841,
        "text": "If we don\u2019t find them, they must have been\nat planet five"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 185841,
        "end_time": 186701,
        "text": "or seven,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 186701,
        "end_time": 189062,
        "text": "meaning they\u2019ll next move to four"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 189062,
        "end_time": 190810,
        "text": "or six."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 190810,
        "end_time": 192951,
        "text": "Let\u2019s now search planet four."
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 192951,
        "end_time": 195990,
        "text": "If they\u2019re not there, they must have gone \nto the sixth planet"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 195990,
        "end_time": 198021,
        "text": "and can only flee to three"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 198021,
        "end_time": 200011,
        "text": "or seven."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 200011,
        "end_time": 203362,
        "text": "If we next scour planet three \nand don\u2019t find them,"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 203362,
        "end_time": 206960,
        "text": "we know they went to planet seven \nand are now cornered."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 206960,
        "end_time": 212710,
        "text": "They can only move to planet six, where\nwe\u2019ll apprehend them on our fifth search."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 212710,
        "end_time": 214561,
        "text": "Of course, this plan only works"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 214561,
        "end_time": 219062,
        "text": "assuming that the rebels were on \nan even-numbered planet in the first hour."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 219062,
        "end_time": 221221,
        "text": "But what if that assumption was wrong?"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 221221,
        "end_time": 224612,
        "text": "In that case, they must\u2019ve started \non an odd-numbered planet."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 224612,
        "end_time": 227904,
        "text": "And because they move to an adjacent \nplanet every hour,"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 227904,
        "end_time": 232931,
        "text": "their location must alternate between\nodd and even-numbered planets."
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 232931,
        "end_time": 235992,
        "text": "This means that if they were on \nan odd-numbered planet to start,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 235992,
        "end_time": 240083,
        "text": "after five moves, they&#39;d be \non an even-numbered planet."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 240083,
        "end_time": 242242,
        "text": "So if our first five searches missed them"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 242242,
        "end_time": 246061,
        "text": "because our assumption that they started \non an even-numbered planet was wrong,"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 246061,
        "end_time": 249883,
        "text": "all we have to do now \nis repeat the sequence!"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 249883,
        "end_time": 251336,
        "text": "Searching the planets in order"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 251336,
        "end_time": 252061,
        "text": "two,"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 252061,
        "end_time": 253501,
        "text": "three,"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 253501,
        "end_time": 254733,
        "text": "four,"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 254733,
        "end_time": 256142,
        "text": "three,"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 256142,
        "end_time": 257350,
        "text": "six,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 257350,
        "end_time": 258621,
        "text": "two,"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 258621,
        "end_time": 259771,
        "text": "three,"
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 259771,
        "end_time": 261132,
        "text": "four,"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 261132,
        "end_time": 262240,
        "text": "three,"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 262240,
        "end_time": 263590,
        "text": "six,"
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 263590,
        "end_time": 265560,
        "text": "leaves the rebels nowhere to run."
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 265560,
        "end_time": 269872,
        "text": "Thanks to your deductive reasoning, \norder is restored to the galaxy."
    }
]